e\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAt the center of the home, the staircase connects the floors with quiet elegance and a dark material palette.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-01.jpg\" alt=\"At the center of the home, the staircase connects the floors with quiet elegance and a dark material palette.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-01-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-01-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-01-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-01-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-01-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-02.jpg\" alt=\"At the center of the home, the staircase connects the floors with quiet elegance and a dark material palette.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-02-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-02-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-02-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-02-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/black-stairs-270525-1057-02-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA standout feature of the home is the sunken basement courtyard, accessed via concrete steps and framed by cast-in-place retaining walls. This private outdoor retreat opens off the recreation room and receives warm southern light.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/sunken-courtyard-270525-1151-01.jpg\" alt=\"A standout feature of this modern home is the sunken basement courtyard, accessed via concrete steps and framed by cast-in-place retaining walls. This private outdoor retreat opens off the recreation room and receives warm southern light.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/sunken-courtyard-270525-1151-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/sunken-courtyard-270525-1151-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/sunken-courtyard-270525-1151-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/sunken-courtyard-270525-1151-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/sunken-courtyard-270525-1151-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe primary bedroom and ensuite bathroom feel both secluded and light-filled, a quiet retreat elevated above the city. The mood is soft and restrained with light walls and decor, and wide oak floors that help to create a calming palette that continues into the ensuite. The bathroom echoes the home’s material language, with travertine surfaces and warm natural light giving the space a refined, spa-like feel.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01.jpg\" alt=\"A modern primary suite with contrasting dark walnut and limestone walls.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01a.jpg\" alt=\"A walk-through closet in a modern primary suite.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01a.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01a-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01a-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01a-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01a-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/primary-bedroom-suite-270525-1142-01a-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\